    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gary Goat RPG! Legend of the Jewel Seeds</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A colorful, turn-based RPG inspired by Super Mario RPG and the SNES era, join Gary and his friends on an adventure to return the legendary Jewel Seeds to the Inner Garden!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Discover Gary's world while navigating isometric style platforming, collecting items and trinkets, and battling for the seven legendary Jewel Seeds. As you gain party members on your journey, you'll help them overcome their own struggles and uncover the mystery of the Jewel Seeds!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Features</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Turn-based, strategic combat</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-2.5D, isometric platforming</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Time-based attacks and a status-focused magic system</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Colorful, retro-style graphics</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-A light-hearted story about friendship</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289360/extras/e5d6ec67426f7995b5c86f2cbc45efee.poster.avif?t=1760341945\" width=394 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289360/extras/e5d6ec67426f7995b5c86f2cbc45efee.webm?t=1760341945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289360/extras/e5d6ec67426f7995b5c86f2cbc45efee.mp4?t=1760341945\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
